		<h2>A History of Collaborative Care</h2><br>
         <p>Established in 2008, The Zeebok Polyclinic's mission has always been to promote the health of our patients with personalized health care.</p>
         <p>Here at The Zeebok Polyclinic, our physicians are in charge. This means they have the power to put you first. It’s a departure in health care philosophy that has attracted some of the area’s most respected physicians. And a difference you’ll feel the moment you walk through the door.</p>
         <br><ul style="padding-left:23px"><li>More than 200 top primary care and specialty physicians and advanced practice clinicians.</li>
                <li>One of the largest multi-specialty clinics in the Barrackpore Sound region.</li>
                <li>More than 3 locations throughout the greater Barrackpore area.</li>
			</ul><br>
        <h2>A Multispecialty, Patient-Focused Team</h2><br>
         <p>Think of The Zeebok Polyclinic as a single doorway to your health care needs. From pediatrics, family practice and internal medicine to specialist physicians and surgeons, The Zeebok Polyclinic team works together with one goal in mind: what’s right for you.</p>
         <br><ul style="padding-left:23px"><li>Primary care focused on prevention, disease management and appropriate clinical interventions</li>
            <li>The top specialist physicians and surgeons across more than two dozen medical specialties, working with your primary care doctor for the most comprehensive care</li>
            <li>On-site services at several locations for your convenience.</li>
         </ul><br>
        <h2>Where Technology Meets Humanity</h2><br>
          <p>The Zeebok Polyclinic embraces state-of-the-art technology, but we never forget the human side of health care.  As a Polyclinic patient, you’ll have access to:</p><br>
          <ul style="padding-left:23px"><li>MyChart – a convenient online tool that empowers you to be a better advocate for your family’s health.  My Chart offers the convenience and flexibility of access to your medical information, anytime.</li>
             <li>Specialties and services that combine prevention, education and treatment.</li>
            <li>Health care that considers the whole person – primary care doctors to manage your health, help you when you’re sick, and work side by side with specialists when needed.</li>
          </ul><br>
